  "text": "Existing work has focused mainly on traditional machine learning problems that are limited to independent and identically distributed (IID) data [CITATION_1] . In addition, Oglic et al. propose interactive kernel PCA [CITATION_2] . Kapoor et al. [CITATION_3] use a humanassisted optimization strategy in the design of multi-class classifiers for iid data.",
